    <title>OpenClaw 安装配置指南</title>
    <link href="https://vinwjin.github.io/posts/2026-03-11-openclaw-setup/"/>
    <id>https://vinwjin.github.io/posts/2026-03-11-openclaw-setup/</id>
    <published>2026-03-10T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-03-10T16:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h2><p>OpenClaw 是一个运行在 NAS 上的 AI 助手框架，支持多种渠道接入（飞书、Telegram 等）。</p><h2 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h2><ul><li>NAS 一台（飞牛NAS）</li><li>Docker</li><li>API Key（MiniMax、OpenAI 等）</li></ul><h2 id="安装步骤"><a href="#安装步骤" class="headerlink" title="安装步骤"></a>安装步骤</h2><h3 id="1-安装-Docker"><a href="#1-安装-Docker" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装 Docker"></a>1. 安装 Docker</h3><p>在飞牛NAS 的应用中心安装 Docker 套件。</p><h3 id="2-拉取镜像"><a href="#2-拉取镜像" class="headerlink" title="2. 拉取镜像"></a>2. 拉取镜像</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull openclaw/openclaw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-运行容器"><a href="#3-运行容器" class="headerlink" title="3. 运行容器"></a>3. 运行容器</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">  --name openclaw \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 8080:8080 \</span><br><span class="line">  -v ~/.openclaw:/data \</span><br><span class="line">  openclaw/openclaw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-配置"><a href="#4-配置" class="headerlink" title="4. 配置"></a>4. 配置</h3><p>编辑 <code>~/.openclaw/config.yaml</code>，配置你的 AI API 和渠道。</p><h2 id="接入飞书"><a href="#接入飞书" class="headerlink" title="接入飞书"></a>接入飞书</h2><ol><li>创建飞书应用</li><li>获取 App ID 和 App Secret</li><li>在配置文件中填写</li><li>添加机器人到群聊</li></ol><hr><p>有问题欢迎留言~</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
